# Assets Directory

This directory contains 3D models, textures, and world data for the RustRide virtual world.

## Structure

- models/ - GLTF/GLB 3D models
  - cyclist.glb - Avatar with cycling animation
  - bikes/ - Bike models (road_bike.glb, tt_bike.glb, gravel_bike.glb)
  - environment/ - Trees, buildings, road segments

- textures/ - PNG textures
  - terrain/ - Ground textures (grass, asphalt, dirt)
  - sky/ - Sky gradient textures
  - objects/ - Object textures

- worlds/ - World definitions and route data
  - countryside/ - Rolling hills world
  - mountains/ - Alpine world
  - coastal/ - Beach/ocean world
